<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Moodify - 마이페이지</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style_mypage.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../frame/header_mypage') %>

  <div class="mypage-container">
    <!-- 프로필 섹션 -->
    <div class="profile-section">
      <div class="profile-card">
        <!-- 프로필 아이콘 -->
        <div class="profile-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 닉네임 -->
        <h2 class="nickname">닉네임</h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 메뉴 리스트 -->
    <div class="menu-section">
      <a href="/info" class="menu-item">
        <span class="menu-text">내 정보 수정</span>
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
      </a>

      <a href="/history" class="menu-item">
        <span class="menu-text">히스토리</span>
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
      </a>

      <a href="/favorites" class="menu-item">
        <span class="menu-text">저장한 음악</span>
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
      </a>

      <a href="/settings" class="menu-item">
        <span class="menu-text">설정</span>
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
      </a>

      <a href="/qna" class="menu-item">
        <span class="menu-text">Q&A</span>
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
      </a>

      <a href="#" class="menu-item logout" id="withdrawBtn">
        <span class="menu-text">탈퇴하기</span>
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
      </a>

      <div class="modal-overlay" id="withdrawModalOverlay">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <h2 class="modal-title">정말 탈퇴하시겠습니까?</h2>
          <p class="modal-text">회원 탈퇴 시 계정 정보, 저장한 음악, 감정 기록, 재생 목록 등 모든 데이터가 즉시 삭제되며 복구할 수 없습니다. 동일한 이메일로 재가입하더라도 이전 데이터는 복원되지 않습니다.</p>
          <div class="modal-buttons">
            <button class="modal-btn continue-btn" id="cancelWithdrawBtn">돌아가기</button>
            <button class="modal-btn delete-btn-modal" id="confirmWithdrawBtn">탈퇴하기</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="/js/mypage.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
